{
  "stem": "1692.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Ukrainian did the killing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But when he called them, he asked them-- what a question to ask. 'Do you believe in God?' In other words, what you see, how can you believe in God?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- but then, about-- I would say about three months later, they rounded up all the young people, put 'em on trucks, took them out of the city, killed them, and buried them in one big, mass grave.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The rest were told to go home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the Ukrainian got those graves ready before.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know there were graves there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were just told to go to a certain place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were hiding.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were hiding in an attic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And a neighbor, who was a Polish woman, she asked this Nazi who in the Ukraine who were there, to come into this house.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She said, I'm sure they're hiding there in the attic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They probably took the ladder with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he wasn't interested.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He kept on going.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were a lot of people there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had some babies there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We had a man who was coughing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we were terrible frightened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But then there was another man outside who was a Ukrainian, a neighbor, a wonderful person.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He knew we were up there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And every time when they went away, the-- the Nazis with the-- the Poles or the Ukrainian, whoever was there, he would cough.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That was a signal to us, you can relax.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And by the end of the day, he came into the house and tell us we can go down-- but not the young people, because they killed all the young people.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we stayed up there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they went down.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
